00:14:36,676 --> 00:14:38,838
What do you mean,
that's the hope?

295
00:14:39,345 --> 00:14:43,578
Well, I'm sure Dr. Gates has
explained that Gabriel's tissues...

296
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:46,117
may be permanently
damaged because of the cold.

297
00:14:46,285 --> 00:14:49,084
I explained that, but we're
trying to think positive here.

298
00:14:49,255 --> 00:14:50,723
Right.

299
00:14:51,591 --> 00:14:55,619
Look, we all hope this brings him
back, but he's been down for a long time.

300
00:14:55,795 --> 00:14:57,889
Did over an hour of CPR.

301
00:14:58,564 --> 00:14:59,964
Celia, call someone.

302
00:15:00,733 --> 00:15:03,794
A friend, family, it doesn't matter.
You just need some support.

303
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:06,098
You don't know what I need.

304
00:15:08,174 --> 00:15:09,403
I'm a single mom.

305
00:15:09,575 --> 00:15:12,704
