306
00:15:17,717 --> 00:15:19,948
Jimmy, Gabriel's dad...

307
00:15:21,754 --> 00:15:24,883
he was one of those guys
who couldn't stay out of trouble.

308
00:15:25,057 --> 00:15:29,085
Running drugs, stealing cars.

309
00:15:29,295 --> 00:15:31,787
I was an idiot. I
thought he'd change.

310
00:15:33,466 --> 00:15:34,593
That's human.

311
00:15:36,469 --> 00:15:41,498
And I told my mom Jimmy and I
were gonna raise the baby together...

312
00:15:41,707 --> 00:15:43,767
and she kicked
me out of the house.

313
00:15:44,710 --> 00:15:46,679
She said, "You may be lost...

314
00:15:46,846 --> 00:15:51,216
but I am not gonna have a guy
