315
00:15:52,318 --> 00:15:54,253
Looking back, she
was probably right.

316
00:15:56,422 --> 00:16:01,156
Celia, there's a very good chance
that Gabriel's heart won't start up again.

317
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:07,664
No, please, please don't
say that. This is gonna work.

318
00:16:11,003 --> 00:16:13,666
Guys, I need another
liter of NS and an ABG kit.

319
00:16:13,873 --> 00:16:15,637
Okay. Yeah, I got it.

320
00:16:15,808 --> 00:16:19,472
And check an ionized calcium while
you're at it. The last one was low.

321
00:16:19,846 --> 00:16:22,714
555-0172.

322
00:16:22,882 --> 00:16:26,751
That's my mom.
Could you call her?

323
00:16:27,253 --> 00:16:29,119
Right away.

324
00:16:38,664 --> 00:16:40,997
Yeah!

