- Oh, no way.

340
00:17:41,193 --> 00:17:42,957
- Way.
- Oh, this explains everything.

341
00:17:43,129 --> 00:17:44,620
Weird behavior, the program...

342
00:17:44,864 --> 00:17:47,197
Ruse to play on this
team and kick your ass.

343
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:50,734
- He's a ringer.
- Yeah, baby, huh?

344
00:17:52,471 --> 00:17:57,603
I had a 26-year-old kid on the
