426
00:23:44,423 --> 00:23:46,221
Never mind.

427
00:23:49,395 --> 00:23:50,624
What are you doing here?

428
00:23:50,829 --> 00:23:52,457
I wanted to let you know...

429
00:23:52,731 --> 00:23:55,394
- You can't be here.
